{
  "ir_hash": "sha256:6cf03ecfc5190d47bc9409cdd958dc8d9b8c1e43a02ae7186db8b7ad7dc16f8e",
  "knowledges": [
    {
      "content": "真空是完全没有阻力的介质（介质密度为零）。",
      "content_hash": "312fa770688155acb317f7ad5d347dbb2711ae8e0d7669353c5f2eb76fd9dcf3",
      "id": "lcn_d9040cb542aec833",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "setting"
    },
    {
      "content": "斜面沟槽经抛光处理，衬以羊皮纸，使用坚硬光滑的青铜球——摩擦和空气阻力可忽略。",
      "content_hash": "1f0bf015094c0e1e12800da494297e5f5c94c3661d889d0cbf208760651bdddc",
      "id": "lcn_967becf10811d482",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "setting"
    },
    {
      "content": "日常生活中，石头比羽毛下落更快，铁球比木球更快。",
      "content_hash": "8499553e7996a31e7e7ca509ea6657455696f32518ac9326479a6c1fd19e16b5",
      "id": "lcn_611d440099b0fba0",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "在不同介质中比较轻重物体的下落，介质越稠密速度差异越明显；越稀薄差异越不明显。",
      "content_hash": "9e090334d4bb55c4b3090d50a016f1e15bbbfeb65ff4c11997260f16137c0ddd",
      "id": "lcn_cc85bf6ddeaf6fb7",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "在空气中，金球、铅球、铜球等重材料球从100腕尺落下，金球领先铜球不超过四指。",
      "content_hash": "00b33ea8900677cdc7959dba51969adf5d49916cdd9a4e47f0676b6d9d974564",
      "id": "lcn_d821c4862cd968b7",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "斜面实验1：不同重量的球沿抛光沟槽滚下，所经距离之比等于时间之比的平方，与球重量无关。",
      "content_hash": "f5afb76d7414671a5b4255085525ba170ab6a5ef2c802512dee11b123317b562",
      "id": "lcn_7ad03407f44fbdc8",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "斜面实验2：重复实验百余次，结果偏差不超过脉搏一次，高度可重复。",
      "content_hash": "faab13fe0630d91c370a8915cd2aab68a9eb6c3168ce37a6b22be1091a101289",
      "id": "lcn_7a542c0f2dfcf2c9",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "物体下落速度与其重量成正比：重物比轻物下落更快。",
      "content_hash": "04d12524a96aa62d944af0e7ea05f62354523b8141297a61293708f5f3893381",
      "id": "lcn_f067c3f8031d47ab",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "A的预测：日常应观察到重者更快。",
      "content_hash": "04cea86cabf66b3f484f2b970423cc0f0c0b4b0777eb4451e46ab2a90477a15b",
      "id": "lcn_00f0f1731a41a613",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "B _daily与O _daily是等价命题：A的预测即日常观察。",
      "content_hash": "ad3cda8b96c188f1024d9b806dcd2eb39c64bed5ca8efe44019b36ab88bc31fd",
      "id": "lcn_b117c15f71a2e1d3",
