      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "假设重物下落更快，将重球H与轻球L绑在一起，L拖拽H，复合体HL速度应慢于H。",
      "content_hash": "72e26582b62753ac3257bba349965004402279d689b38c34e24366f2e2a9681b",
      "id": "lcn_fb2245ed6b7cd8be",
      "local_members": null,
      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "假设重物下落更快，复合体HL总重量大于H，因此HL速度应快于H。",
      "content_hash": "ce41006a5f51d974da97d430761daea3fddd82704db95476d83b0c82a14b9ae5",
      "id": "lcn_0c4b4ddf8d0d747f",
