      "metadata": null,
      "package_id": "galileo_fine",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": null,
      "representative_lcn": null,
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "T1与T2互相矛盾：复合体HL不能同时慢于H又快于H。",
